@startuml CP Relay Scoring & Assignment
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5

title DVConf — Control Plane: Relay Scoring & Room Assignment

participant "CP Daemon" as CP
database "Sui Chain" as Chain
participant "Relay\nDaemon(s)" as Relay
participant "Signaling\nDaemon(s)" as Sig

== Daemon Registration (Startup) ==

Relay -> Chain : relay_registry::register_relay(\n  region, endpoint_url, mode)
Chain --> Relay : RelayRegistered event

Sig -> Chain : signaling_registry::register_signaling(\n  region, endpoint_url)
Chain --> Sig : SignalingRegistered event

CP -> Chain : control_plane_registry::register_cp()
Chain --> CP : CPRegistered event

== Heartbeat Loop ==

loop Every 30s
  Relay -> Chain : relay_registry::update_load(\n  registry, cap, current_room_count)
  Chain --> Relay : RelayLoadUpdated event

  Sig -> Chain : signaling_registry::update_load(\n  registry, cap, connection_count)
  Chain --> Sig : SignalingLoadUpdated event

  CP -> Chain : control_plane_registry::heartbeat(\n  registry, cp_cap)
end

== CP Event Processing ==

CP -> Chain : poll RelayRegistered events
Chain --> CP : new relay info
CP -> CP : relayState[relay_id] = {\n  region, endpoint, reputation,\n  rtt: 0, load: 0, stake }

CP -> Chain : poll RelayLoadUpdated events
Chain --> CP : load updates
CP -> CP : relayState[relay_id].load = new_load

CP -> Chain : poll RelayRTTUpdated events
Chain --> CP : rtt updates (validator-probed)
CP -> CP : relayState[relay_id].rtt = new_rtt

note over CP
  RTT is **never self-reported**.
  Only validator-probed values
  (written by economic_layer
  after SessionProof submission)
end note

== Room Created → Scoring ==

CP -> Chain : poll RoomCreated events
Chain --> CP : RoomCreated(room_id, relay_mode)

CP -> CP : Filter relays by mode (SFU/MCU)

loop For each eligible relay
  CP -> CP : score = \n  0.30 × reputation +\n  0.25 × (1/rtt) +\n  0.20 × (1/load) +\n  0.15 × (stake/max_stake) +\n  0.10 × region_match
end

CP -> CP : best_relay = max(scores)
CP -> CP : best_signaling = min(load)

CP -> Chain : room_manager::assign_relay_and_signaling(\n  net_reg, manager, cp_cap,\n  room_id, best_relay, best_signaling)
Chain --> CP : RoomAssigned event\n(room_id, relay_id, signaling_id)

@enduml
